               <provenance>The name of the donor is in all probability
                     Walda Dāwit (it appears in the supplication formulas on 18ra, 18vb, 21ra, 27va, 29va, 30rb, etc. as well as in Additio 1),
                     possibly one of the "children of Habta Māryām". Other names appear in the
                     supplication formulas throughout Walda Giyorgi[s], Walda Libānos, ʾElyas, Walda
                     Krǝstos, Mäḥare Krǝstos, Ṭǝʿǝmtä Māryām, Kǝfla Māryām, Gila Māryām (65va), Gǝddä Māryām (132va), Kǝbǝrtä Māryām, Qǝddǝstä Krǝstos, Gabra Giyorgis, Habta
                     Māryām.</provenance></history>
